醫生</blockquote><br />\n我都希望係單純中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉 就係google左好多病但係都好似唔太關事<br />\n唔知點好宜家"},{"pid":"c9adcfc32f617e083e75794dd0182d2607ef092e","tid":120932,"uid":81277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有試過，突然幾秒係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c32badd1a771a45a60b77fba2372693d8f13cd","tid":120932,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有啲中二病味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係真可以Google完睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n我都希望係單純中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉 就係google左好多病但係都好似唔太關事<br />\n唔知點好宜家</blockquote><br />\n等我搵下先<br />\n利申google好撚叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.healthcommunities.com/memory-problems/senior-moments-dementia_jhmwp.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthcommunities.com%2Fmemory-problems%2Fsenior-moments-dementia_jhmwp.shtml&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=842e07de\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.healthcommunities.com/memory-problems/senior-moments-dementia_jhmwp.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\nBut other types of memory loss, such as forgetting appointments or becoming <span style=\"color: red;\">momentarily disoriented in a familiar place, may indicate <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">mild cognitive impairment</span>.</span> In <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">dementia</span></span>&mdash;the most serious form of memory impairment&mdash;people often find themselves <span style=\"color: blue;\">disoriented in time and place and unable to name common objects or recognize once-familiar people</span>"},{"pid":"cea43c66e164a18ed69eba3449a99b309a488a9b","tid":120932,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"Butterfly effect"},{"pid":"a309933ef2895bcd2c075819e644bfc49324a5af","tid":120932,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"Vascular dementia<br />\n<br />\nsigns of vascular dementia may appear suddenly. This is because the memory loss and confusion are caused by strokes or changes in the blood supply to the brain. If the strokes stop, you may get better or stay the same for a long time. If you have more strokes, you may get worse.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nia.nih.gov/alzheimers/publication/understanding-memory-loss/serious-memory-problems-causes-and-treatments\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nia.nih.gov%2Falzheimers%2Fpublication%2Funderstanding-memory-loss%2Fserious-memory-problems-causes-and-treatments&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=0204793d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nia.nih.gov/alzheimers/publication/understanding-memory-loss/serious-memory-problems-causes-and-treatments</a>"},{"pid":"f2dab1507b725aea97db064d28f88a1e95aa7e23","tid":120932,"uid":81277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Vascular dementia<br />\n<br />\nsigns of vascular dementia may appear suddenly. This is because the memory loss and confusion are caused by strokes or changes in the blood supply to the brain. If the strokes stop, you may get better or stay the same for a long time. If you have more strokes, you may get worse.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nia.nih.gov/alzheimers/publication/understanding-memory-loss/serious-memory-problems-causes-and-treatments\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nia.nih.gov%2Falzheimers%2Fpublication%2Funderstanding-memory-loss%2Fserious-memory-problems-causes-and-treatments&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=0204793d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nia.nih.gov/alzheimers/publication/understanding-memory-loss/serious-memory-problems-causes-and-treatments</a></blockquote><br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe4b9c77dd6dd4510423c34f68e79b805635361","tid":120932,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐得太耐起身太急頭暈之後就唔記得自己係邊個 依家係邊到 好似第三人稱睇緊個世界咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯就係類似咁嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我居然覺得個感覺好爽皮"},{"pid":"fbb6fa6c307167f5750805252717ce7cb68ac467","tid":120932,"uid":36845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"明顯係個腦有d事<br />\n快d睇醫生"}]}